I have also worked with Altran Technologies and Orange OBS as a Java Software Engineer. In these roles, I developed configuration tools for home automation equipment, managed network equipment for Orange OBS customers, and collaborated with international teams. I have experience working with Java 8, Spring, Maven, and various other technologies.
My technical skills include Java, Python, SQL, and a wide range of frameworks and architectures like JEE, Spring Boot, and Microservices. I'm also proficient in databases such as Oracle, MySQL, and MongoDB, and have experience with version control using GIT and SVN. I am well-versed in Agile methodologies, including Scrum and Kanban.
